name: Barely Qualified(Your a janitor :/)
description:
Weave, dodge, and Dash through hoards of... Robots?? ON YOUR FIRST DAY OF JANITOR DUTY! 

  • Left Click --- Shoot
  • Right Click --- Summon Barrier
  • Left Shift --- Dash

This is a very early in development prototype! I'm only uploading this to see if others find the general gameplay and visual style fun. Any and all feedback is welcome!
